item.title: Who We Are
item.dc:creator: techteam
item.content:encoded: we established this company in 1989. We opened our first office in London at the end of June, 1997 and were soon joined by a large number that came from other parts to work on technology projects here. Today we have offices around the world - Canada, Germany, Australia.

item.title: Hello world!
item.dc:creator: techteam
item.content:encoded: Welcome to Previews Sites. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: Hi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard. Commenter avatars come from Gravatar.

item.title: John Smith
item.dc:creator: techteam
item.content:encoded: I also enjoyed hydro therapy for the first time. I learned that there is a difference between being sick and having to resort with lots of water in order go on vacation; people who suffer from severe dehydration could do it at any hour, without leaving their homes or even getting out of bed as we were going around town by foot.

item.title: Jennifer Lohan
item.dc:creator: techteam
item.content:encoded: I enjoyed aroma therapy and they were really helpful, but I will recommend just getting a cup of tea or coffee before doing any treatments as you won't be able to identify the correct odor without going down into your nostrils.
